Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie: Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh! Oh, my gosh!\NOh, my gosh! Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh! Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Twilight,\Nwhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in here, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never guess\Nwhat I just got!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard a lot of "Oh, my\Ngosh-in'" and we weren't sure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,if it was a good thing\Nor a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"To Pink Pony who lives\Nwith baked goods."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yaks cordially invite Pink\NPony to Yikslerbertfest."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come. NOW!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford is officially\Ninviting me to Yikslerbertfest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in Yakyakistan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is "Yikslerbertfest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sacred\NYak holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get Prince\NRutherford to invite you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I subtly hinted for an\Ninvitation in my letters to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} May I please come{\i0}\N{\i1} to Yikslerbertfest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Pretty please?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Pretty please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Pretty please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Pretty, pretty, pretty,{\i0}\N{\i1} pretty, pretty please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After my seventeenth scroll,\NI think he picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what I was putting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee hee hee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we still don't\Nknow a lot about the yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think you should definitely\Ngo to Yikslerbertfest, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fostering friendships\Nis what ponies do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to be the Official\NFriendship Ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's not an\Nofficial position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Princess\Nof Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make\Nit happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. You have to\Nmake it OFFICIAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I hereby\Nmake Pinkie Pie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the Official Friendship\NAmbassador to the Yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}officially{\i0}  the most\Nexciting day of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo, Gummy! Pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of an\NOfficial Friendship Ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Road Trip Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, I spy with my\Nofficial friendship eye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way, the\Nanswer was "sky." I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that was\Na hard one, Gummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best Official\NFriendship Travel Companion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All : Yaks destroy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! Pink Pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to [crash] er..\Nbe here, Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[crash] Uh, did something\Nterrible happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Yikslerbertfest canceled!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This Yikslerbertfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where yaks get\Ntogether to stomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhh, I didn't know that was\Npart of the sacred holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So this angry display\Nof destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. And here I thought you yaks\Nwere just in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Stomping relaxes yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak's head never been so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is AWESOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony better check\Nself before wreck self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That is century-old sacred\NYak Twig passed down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,from generation to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gasp!] Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to get into\Nthe spirit of Yikslerbertfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[whining] Maybe I can fix\Nit--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha! Yak kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak got Pink Pony good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Horn bump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure did,\NPrince Rutherford!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close\None, Gummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This trip has to\Nbe perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we're not\Njust visiting as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on Official Friendship\NAmbassador business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Less talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,More stomping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie: Yeah! Uh! Stomp! Stomp! Stomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I take Pink Pony\Non Yakyakistan tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Prince Rutherford.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. I've been to\NYakyakistan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But thought Pink Pony\Nmight not recognize town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,since decorated for\NYikslerbertfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so different now that\Nyou've pointed it out. Heh, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yaks not just have\Neye for decorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks also amazing builders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you hired\Nprofessional contractors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me help\Nyou with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This Ceremonial Yak Fire pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where yaks tell stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so much to officially\Ntell the ponies when I get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This Yak Eating Hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hut where yaks eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, the perfect balance\Nof vanilla extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks grow own vanilla bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing imported.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak Sleeping Hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hut where yaks sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak Music Hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hut where yaks enjoy\Nbeautiful music.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beautiful and-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sssh. Pink Pony\Nruin with talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,... And that how yaks\Ndefeat evil and save world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony like yak story!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ha! Yak impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony can almost\Nbe Honorary Yak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Official Friendship\NAmbassador and Honorary Yak!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony's title\Ncard is full!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Horn bump!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, I don't have a horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford, can I\Nget some honorary yak horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Yak horn too heavy\Nfor small pony head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikslerbertfest Stomp Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stomp harder, yaks extra happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies and yaks, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this part of the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony ask too\Nmany questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is buried in snow!\NWhat are we going to do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[mumbles] Yaks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow fall from\Nmountains all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Every Yikslerbertfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Avalanches like\Nthis completely bury
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all your homes every\NYikslerbertfest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This.. is.. big avalanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But not a problem,\Nfor yaks are tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks dig through snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good, you have an\Nemergency plan in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo, I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We must be almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still snow\Neverywhere!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks keep digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhhhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks stop digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes situation worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, don't worry,\NPrince Rutherford.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to Ponyville\Nand ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight and the others will be\Nhappy to come dig the snow away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, many hooves\Nmake light work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Gummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks no need pony help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, I'm sure\Nit'll be OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,cause you probably\Nhave a plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yaks wait\Nfor snow to melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All this snow!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take a thousand\Nmoons before it melts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks known for their patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.. be that as it may, in\Nthe meantime, what will you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bah! Yaks can make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardship make yaks the\Nstrong yaks that yaks are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If Pink Pony disagrees, then she\Ncan leave Yakyakistan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and never return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Er.. of course Pink Pony\Nagrees with you! Heheh..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's try out\Nsome snow recipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, heh..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks can make this work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawn] Yak tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak retire to new Sleeping Hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow cake good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the right balance\Nof cold and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak eating new Eating Hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Psst, Prince Rutherford,\Nwhat are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This New Music Hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So we're swaying to... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssshhh. Pink Pony ruin snow\Nmusic with talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was yak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak stomach rumbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sshh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Yak will\Nhear yak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But snow worse\Nthan yak ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak hungry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp!] Gummy, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks stop swaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Music over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If Twilight and the others\Nknew what was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,they would be here to help\Nin a pony's heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to convince\NPrince Rutherford
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that asking for help is OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help me, Gummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And see, asking you to\Nhelp wasn't hard at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony has\Ngathered you around
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the New Ceremonial\NYak Firepit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,... to tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A yak tradition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a story\Nabout a group of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,er.. goats, who live\Nin the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a sandstorm\Nand their entire village
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,was buried in sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing they could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew they could not survive\Non only eating sand-wiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, finally, the goat's\Nbrave, wise leader
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--let's just call\Nhim Prince er.. Drutherford-- heh, heh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,decides that they couldn't\Ndo it by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So he asked the neighboring\Ntown of uh, Bovineville
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to come help them. Yeah! Cows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The magical cows\Nhelped the goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone survived and\Nlived happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they asked for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the\Nmoral of that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it A: asking for\Nhelp is OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,B: asking for help\Nsaves the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Or C: asking for help\Nis good for everypony!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,D: goats weak\Nand horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic Bovines need to stay\Nout of goats' business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Any-yak wanna shout\Nout another answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie: Hey,\NPrince Rutherford.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you about\Nsomething -- what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh.. Yak snow bed got a\Nlittle melty last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want\Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, these yak snow\Nbeds are the fluffiest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ever slept in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so comfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you forget that it's just\Na cold block of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the yak snow\Nsandwiches, mmm, mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it when food\Nburns your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or overwhelms\Nit with flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yak hates that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who would\Nreally, really enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,these snow sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle and\Nthe other ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I go to Ponyville\Nand bring them back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies like snow sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ponies love snow\Nsandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And, hey, while they're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you can ask if they'll\Nclear the snow away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When Prince was little yak,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince stomped on\Nground too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Made deep hole and\Nfell into hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice froze over hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince waved to friends and\Nfamily from inside frozen hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Waited for spring thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince survived on own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent the whole\Nwinter in a hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And yak never\Nask for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, first of all, how did you\Nmake such a deep hole
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,from stomping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And how did it\Nfreeze over so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And how could you see\Nyour family and friends
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to wave to them from\Ninside a frozen hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if all that was possible,\Nhow did you breathe in there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,YAKS DON'T ASK FOR HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the yaks are hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And who knows when\Nthe snow will melt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't\Nunderstand why--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, is clear now that Pink\NPony does not understand Yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honorary Yak status rescinded!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang! Pretend there\Nis door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just slammed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, be stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Those yaks are so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They refuse to ask for help\Neven though they need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this Official\NFriendship Ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to take matters\Ninto her own hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Gummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A road trip game would\Nofficially calm me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play "Twenty\NMillion Questions."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll ask you twenty\Nmillion questions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,until I can come up with\Nwhat you're thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it green?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it red?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it greenish-red?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it reddish-blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bigger than a bread box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it smaller than a bread box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a bread box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Granny Smith's dentures?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a rooster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a red rooster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a red rooster eating corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhp, used up all twenty\Nmillion questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, we're here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Official Pony\NBalloon still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony gone because Pink\NPony not tough like yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Horn bump in agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleagh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow sandwich lose novelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow couscous for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Prince Rutherford\Nsaid -- Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend there is door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just slammed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So then Pink\NPony said --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, be stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, we have\Nto help the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So in conclusion, we\Nhave to help the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go with it, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be happy to\Nhelp the yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what friendship\Nis all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'll bring\Napples.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This season's batch\Nare extra juicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I shall provide the yaks
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with Equestria's\Nfinest textiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be silky and\Nwarm with hints of gold
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to compliment their horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't bring the\Nyaks any pony stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The yaks are very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what they say, you\Ncan lead a yak to water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but you better not let\Nhim know you're doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,OK then, this will be an
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Official Covert\NFriendship Mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash: You got it!\NPinkie Pie: Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie: Is it yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it slimy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it slimy-yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash: We're\Nnot playing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we have to\Ninfiltrate the yak compound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These walls are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaking in will not be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it's super easy\Ncause I'm awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. I'll\Ncatch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You all know\Nwhat to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow melted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! Yaks tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo-weee, helping to fix\Nan entire yak village
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sure takes a lot out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here\Nbefore--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince: Oh Pink Pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just play it cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't help fix\NYakyakistan! No no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just here for\Nthe snow sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. then we got here and the\Nsnow's gone so we thought
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd hit a diner on the way\Nback to Ponyville. Buh Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Yak not mad\Nat Pink Pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony helped yaks\Nwithout yaks asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Means Pink Pony understand yaks.
